description: Removes tags from the specified Firehose stream. Removed tags are deleted, and you can't recover them after this operation successfully completes. If you specify a tag that doesn't exist, the operation ignores it. This operation has a limit of five transactions per second per account.

parameters.name: DeliveryStreamName
parameters.description: The name of the Firehose stream.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: A list of tag keys. Each corresponding tag is removed from the delivery stream. (string) ---
